_sText:
This map is a css coop fun map with hdr, the objective is to destroy as many boxes as you can, to know how many you have destroyed just
check your score.
Do not kill the other players, unless you want to ruin the game, just wait until they die killed by the boxes.

If you want to play it alone with bots, create a server and add bots and write bot_dont_shoot 1 in console.

As this they will rarely hit with their knives.

To install just unzip in your css/maps directory, everything is bspzipped inside!

Then join or create a server and have fun!

This map is better with some friends that on a server, cause people often just ruins the game by killing everyone.

***IMPORTANT***

Known Issue : If you let too many boxes to spawn, it will crash the game.

Solution : Destroy as many boxes as you can.
